text: Maulana Syed Nasib Ali Shah was a Pakistani politician who served as members of the 12th National Assembly of Pakistan from 16 November 2002 – until his death 22 January 2007. ==References== Category:2007 deaths Category:Pakistani Islamic religious leaders Category:Pakistani Sunni Muslims Category:People from Bannu District Category:Pakistani MNAs 2002–2007 Category:Jamiat Ulema-e- Islam politicians
